WEBVTT

00:01.035 --> 00:03.304
* DA, DA, DA-BA-DA, DA, DA,
BA-DA-BA-DA-BA *

00:03.337 --> 00:04.805
* DA, DA, DA-BA-DA, DA, DA
LET'S GO!

00:04.838 --> 00:06.474
* WE'LL BE THERE

00:06.507 --> 00:09.143
* A WINK AND A SMILE
AND A GREAT OLD TIME *

00:09.177 --> 00:11.345
* YEAH, WE'LL BE THERE

00:11.379 --> 00:13.481
* WHEREVER WE ARE,
THERE'S SOME FUN TO BE FOUND *

00:13.514 --> 00:15.816
* WE'LL BE THERE
WHEN YOU TURN THAT CORNER *

00:15.849 --> 00:17.151
* WE'LL JUMP OUT THE BUSH

00:17.185 --> 00:18.819
* WITH A BIG BEAR HUG
AND A SMILE *

00:18.852 --> 00:20.254
* WE'LL BE THERE

00:29.530 --> 00:32.566
I KNOW I'VE SAID IT BEFORE,
BUT I REALLY MEAN IT THIS TIME.

00:32.600 --> 00:34.001
I'M IN LOVE.

00:34.034 --> 00:35.002
NO WAY, MAN.
THAT'S AWESOME.

00:35.035 --> 00:36.204
WHO'S THE LUCKY GIRL?

00:36.237 --> 00:38.005
THE BAGGER
AT THE GROCERY STORE.

00:38.038 --> 00:39.840
DID YOU SEE THE WAY
SHE LOOKED AT ME?

00:39.873 --> 00:41.242
IS SHE THAT GIRL
WITH THE SHORT HAIR?

00:41.275 --> 00:42.510
OH, NO,
THAT WAS ANOTHER GIRL

00:42.543 --> 00:44.011
THAT I WAS IN LOVE WITH
LAST WEEK.

00:44.044 --> 00:45.346
WHOA. WHOA, WHOA.
STOP. BACK UP.

00:45.379 --> 00:47.848
BEEP. BEEP.
BEEP. BEEP.

00:47.881 --> 00:49.517
[ LAUGHS ] A YARD SALE!

00:49.550 --> 00:51.352
LET'S CHECK IT OUT.

00:51.385 --> 00:52.753
HMM.

00:52.786 --> 00:54.922
WHOA!
A SMASH BROGAN ACTION FIGURE.

00:54.955 --> 00:56.023
SWEET!

00:56.056 --> 00:57.858
GET READY FOR PAIN!

00:57.891 --> 00:58.926
HUH? WHAT THE...

00:58.959 --> 01:00.361
$5?

01:00.394 --> 01:01.195
AW, MAN.

01:01.229 --> 01:03.864
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

01:03.897 --> 01:05.399
THE PERFECT PANORAMA SHOT.

01:05.433 --> 01:08.736
HEY, YOU KNOW, THIS STUFF ISN'T
JUST GOOD FOR PICTURES.

01:08.769 --> 01:10.070
SO WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING FOR,
BEAR?

01:10.104 --> 01:11.372
CAN I HELP YOU
WITH SOMETHING?

01:11.405 --> 01:12.940
OH, UM...
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]

01:12.973 --> 01:14.542
NOTHING REALLY.
JUST LOOKING.

01:14.575 --> 01:15.543
WELL, OKAY THEN.

01:15.576 --> 01:16.710
JUST HOLLER
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING.

01:16.744 --> 01:18.912
UH, OKAY.

01:21.582 --> 01:22.783
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

01:22.816 --> 01:24.918
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

01:24.952 --> 01:26.887
HMM, TINY BASKETBALL?

01:26.920 --> 01:27.888
TOO TINY.

01:27.921 --> 01:28.956
SPRINGY THING?

01:28.989 --> 01:31.392
UH, TOO SPRINGY.

01:31.425 --> 01:32.593
HUH?

01:34.928 --> 01:36.897
THANK YOU, SIR.
YOU ENJOY.

01:36.930 --> 01:38.766
UH, EXCUSE ME.
[ GRUNTS ]

01:38.799 --> 01:39.900
IS THIS BOX REALLY FREE?

01:39.933 --> 01:41.235
WELL, SURE.
TAKE IT.

01:41.269 --> 01:43.070
JUST LOTS OF STUFF IN THERE
NOBODY WANTS.

01:43.103 --> 01:44.738
LESS FOR ME TO THROW AWAY.

01:44.772 --> 01:47.074
REALLY?

01:47.107 --> 01:49.310
Dude, free stuff.

01:50.110 --> 01:52.613
Psst!
Free stuff.

01:59.019 --> 02:00.421
All: FREE STUFF!

02:00.454 --> 02:01.822
[ LAUGHTER ]

02:01.855 --> 02:04.758
ALL RIGHT, GUYS. START CALLING
DIBS ON WHATEVER YOU WANT.

02:04.792 --> 02:06.427
-WHOA!
-WHOA!

02:06.460 --> 02:08.996
[ LAUGHS ] MINE!

02:09.029 --> 02:10.598
SMASH HANDS.

02:10.631 --> 02:11.832
AWESOME!

02:11.865 --> 02:12.933
HYAH!

02:12.966 --> 02:14.134
CUSHION SMASH!

02:14.168 --> 02:16.136
WHOA! LOOK AT THIS.
AND OLD PHONE.

02:16.170 --> 02:18.472
LOOK IT DOES THIS
FLIP-SLIDY THING.

02:18.506 --> 02:19.507
[ BEEP ]

02:19.540 --> 02:20.474
HYAH!

02:20.508 --> 02:21.942
OH, MY GOSH.
IT JUST TURNED ON.

02:21.975 --> 02:23.177
IT'S STILL WORKING.

02:23.211 --> 02:24.612
WELL, LET'S SEE
IF THE CAMERA WORKS.

02:24.645 --> 02:25.613
WHOA! HYAH!

02:25.646 --> 02:26.614
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

02:26.647 --> 02:29.116
[ LAUGHS ]
IT'S SO PIXELY.

02:29.149 --> 02:31.018
ICE BEAR WILL TAKE
FAMILY ENTERTAINMENT.

02:31.051 --> 02:32.786
FAMILY ENTERTAINMENT SMASH!

02:32.820 --> 02:33.954
PANDA SMASH!

02:33.987 --> 02:35.189
WHAT THE HECK, GRIZZ?!

02:35.223 --> 02:36.790
GO OUTSIDE
IF YOU'RE GONNA SMASH STUFF!

02:36.824 --> 02:38.959
[ LAUGHS ] TIME TO
SHOW THE WORLD MY NEW FORM.

02:38.992 --> 02:39.960
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

02:39.993 --> 02:41.128
OOPS.
LAMP SMASH!

02:41.161 --> 02:43.130
GET OUT!
GOING.

02:43.163 --> 02:46.066
[ DOOR KNOB RATTLES ]

02:47.835 --> 02:48.802
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

02:48.836 --> 02:50.671
WHAT?

02:52.005 --> 02:53.407
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

02:54.408 --> 02:57.177
[ VIBRATING CONTINUES ]

03:02.583 --> 03:03.817
UH, I-I GOT TO GO.

03:03.851 --> 03:04.818
DON'T BOTHER ME!

03:04.852 --> 03:06.754
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

03:15.028 --> 03:17.498
Woman:
TODAY IS A SPECIAL DAY.

03:17.531 --> 03:20.200
TODAY,
YOU START FOCUSING ON YOU.

03:20.234 --> 03:23.404
TODAY, YOUR CYCLES
AND THE EARTH'S ARE ONE.

03:23.437 --> 03:25.205
HI, THERE.
AND WELCOME TO...

03:25.239 --> 03:26.507
[ UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYS ]

03:26.540 --> 03:29.243
..."THE PREGNANT WOMEN'S
WORKOUT."

03:29.277 --> 03:31.011
AND WE'RE GONNA SHOW YOU
THAT JUST BECAUSE

03:31.044 --> 03:33.681
YOU'RE PACKING ON SOME
EXTRA POUNDS EATING FOR TWO,

03:33.714 --> 03:37.885
DOESN'T MEAN YOU CAN'T STILL BE
ACTIVE AND STAY FIT.

03:37.918 --> 03:39.086
Grizz: AND THAT! [ LAUGHS ]

03:39.119 --> 03:40.254
TAKE THAT, BAD GUY.

03:40.288 --> 03:42.089
AND THIS AND THIS AND THAT.

03:42.122 --> 03:43.357
WHAT'S THAT?

03:43.391 --> 03:45.025
WELL THEN TAKE THAT,
BAD GUY'S FRIEND.

03:45.058 --> 03:46.360
[ LAUGHS ] OH.

03:46.394 --> 03:48.529
NOW, WHAT HAVEN'T I PUNCHED YET?

03:48.562 --> 03:50.864
OH, THE AFTERNOON POST IS HERE.

03:50.898 --> 03:52.566
HUH?
[ GRUNTS ]

03:52.600 --> 03:55.769
HUH. GUESS I SHOULD
TAKE THESE GLOVES OFF FIRST.

03:55.803 --> 03:58.406
[ GRUNTING ]

04:00.274 --> 04:03.411
OH. OOPS. UH...
THERE YOU GO. GOOD AS NEW.

04:03.444 --> 04:05.746
OKAY.
TIME TO GET THESE OFF FOR REAL.

04:05.779 --> 04:08.215
[ GRUNTING ]

04:08.248 --> 04:09.583
OKAY.
I'M GONNA NEED SOME HELP.

04:09.617 --> 04:13.220
AND STEP AND STEP
AND STEP AND STEP.

04:13.253 --> 04:15.222
KEEP THOSE KNEES UP, LADIES.

04:15.255 --> 04:16.624
OH, COME ON!

04:16.657 --> 04:18.426
MAN!
UH, BROTHER!

04:18.459 --> 04:20.928
[ UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYS ]
HEY! HEY! HEY!

04:20.961 --> 04:22.296
HEY!
ONE AND TWO AND ONE...

04:22.330 --> 04:23.731
[ SIGHS ] GOT TO FIND HELP
SOMEWHERE ELSE.

04:23.764 --> 04:25.799
Panda:
THAT TEXT COULDN'T BE FOR ME.

04:25.833 --> 04:27.935
I MEAN, IT JUST
DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

04:27.968 --> 04:30.738
BUT MAYBE SHE DOES REALLY WANT
TO GO ON A DATE.

04:30.771 --> 04:33.273
EH, MAYBE IF I GIVE HER
ONE LITTLE TEXT BACK.

04:33.307 --> 04:34.742
NO! I SHOULDN'T!

04:34.775 --> 04:36.243
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]
HUH?

04:36.276 --> 04:39.580
"SO, OUR DATE?
LET ME KNOW IF YOU CAN ASAP.

04:39.613 --> 04:42.916
IF YOU CAN'T,
I'LL MAKE OTHER PLANS..."

04:42.950 --> 04:44.251
OUR DATE?

04:44.284 --> 04:45.753
OUR DATE!

04:45.786 --> 04:46.754
[ LAUGHS ]

04:46.787 --> 04:48.322
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT!
A DATE!

04:48.356 --> 04:50.591
OH, WAIT!
WHA-WHAT DO YOU WRITE BACK?

04:50.624 --> 04:53.794
UH, OKAY. I GOT TO WRITE
THE PERFECT RESPONSE...

04:53.827 --> 04:55.596
[ KEYS CLACKING ]

04:55.629 --> 04:56.930
UM...

04:56.964 --> 04:58.599
NO, NOT CLASSY ENOUGH.

04:58.632 --> 05:00.267
SOMETHING PLAYFUL, MAYBE...

05:00.300 --> 05:01.535
[ BEEP ]

05:03.170 --> 05:04.438
NO!

05:04.472 --> 05:06.139
THE PHONE'S DEAD!
THE PHONE'S DEAD!

05:06.173 --> 05:08.008
I NEED A CHARGER!
I NEED A CHARGER QUICK!

05:08.041 --> 05:09.777
NO!
IT'S NOT FITTING!

05:09.810 --> 05:12.012
BREATHE IN, BREATHE OUT.
BREATHE IN, BREATHE OUT.

05:12.045 --> 05:14.948
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]
NOW WE'RE GONNA ADD
AND EXTRA STEP.

05:14.982 --> 05:17.117
THIS MOVE IS FOR
ADVANCED USERS ONLY.

05:17.150 --> 05:18.118
ARE YOU READY?

05:18.151 --> 05:19.119
ICE BEAR IS READY.

05:19.152 --> 05:20.621
OKAY, AND HOP.

05:20.654 --> 05:22.289
WHOO!

05:22.322 --> 05:23.957
OKAY, AND HOP.

05:23.991 --> 05:26.660
WHOO!
GREAT JOB.

05:30.398 --> 05:33.801
UM, EXCUSE ME.

05:33.834 --> 05:35.135
EXCUSE ME, SIR?

05:35.168 --> 05:36.470
UH, COULD YOU, UM...

05:36.504 --> 05:37.638
AAH! HEY, MAN.
I DON'T WANT ANY TROUBLE.

05:37.671 --> 05:39.339
CHILL, OKAY?
SIR, PLEASE!

05:39.373 --> 05:40.808
I JUST NEED SOME HELP!

05:40.841 --> 05:41.975
[ SIGHS ]

05:42.009 --> 05:43.010
OH, HELLO, MA'AM.

05:43.043 --> 05:44.645
WOULD YOU BE SO KIND AS TO --

05:44.678 --> 05:47.047
[ SCREAMS ]
JUST TAKE MY PURSE. AAAH!

05:47.080 --> 05:49.149
NO, I'M NOT TRYING
TO ROB YOU.

05:49.182 --> 05:50.150
I'M A NICE GUY!

05:50.183 --> 05:51.218
[ COINS CLATTER ]
OOPS.

05:51.251 --> 05:53.654
[ UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYS ]

05:53.687 --> 05:55.989
CHARGING CABLE, CHARGING CABLE,
CHARGING -- IS THIS --

05:56.023 --> 05:58.325
NO, COME ON.
COME ON.

05:58.358 --> 06:00.828
[ LAUGHS ]

06:00.861 --> 06:02.696
[ BEEPING ]

06:03.864 --> 06:06.066
OKAY.
I GOT TO DO THIS RIGHT.

06:06.099 --> 06:07.701
[ KEYS CLACKING ]

06:10.103 --> 06:11.371
[ BEEP ]

06:14.041 --> 06:16.510
Woman: TWO MORE TOE TOUCHES.
COME ON.

06:16.544 --> 06:18.712
GREAT JOB, LADIES.

06:18.746 --> 06:21.014
NOW REMEMBER,
WORKING OUT AT HOME IS GREAT,

06:21.048 --> 06:23.751
BUT THE BEST WAY TO EXERCISE IS
TO SHARE A POWER WALK

06:23.784 --> 06:26.086
WITH A FUN GROUP
OF POWERFUL WOMEN.

06:26.119 --> 06:28.722
HMM...

06:28.756 --> 06:34.094
* TOOK A FLIGHT JUST TO GIVE US
THIS DREAM OF MINE *

06:34.127 --> 06:36.530
* CAN A MAN COME THIS FAR...

06:36.564 --> 06:37.865
PLEASE, SOMEONE HELP?

06:37.898 --> 06:38.899
HUH?

06:38.932 --> 06:41.101
OH, THANK GOODNESS.
LAW ENFORCEMENT.

06:41.134 --> 06:42.102
I NEED YOUR HELP.

06:42.135 --> 06:43.403
CAN YOU TAKE THESE HANDS OFF ME?

06:43.437 --> 06:45.873
OF COURSE. RIGHT AFTER
WE SET UP OUR TABLE.

06:45.906 --> 06:47.074
OH, THANK YOU SO MUCH.

06:47.107 --> 06:48.208
OOPS!

06:48.241 --> 06:49.376
OH, LET ME GET IT.
HERE YOU GO.

06:49.409 --> 06:50.410
[ GASPS ]

06:50.444 --> 06:52.079
HEY,
WHAT'D YOU DO THAT FOR?

06:52.112 --> 06:53.747
UH, SORRY. I DIDN'T MEAN TO.
I WAS JUST --

06:53.781 --> 06:55.716
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU YELLING
AT THESE GIRLS FOR?

06:55.749 --> 06:56.717
I'M NOT YELLING.

06:56.750 --> 06:57.918
I JUST --
IT'S THESE GLOVES. THEY --

06:57.951 --> 07:00.053
THE MONSTER
IS BREAKING OUR COOKIES!

07:00.087 --> 07:02.055
THE MONSTER HATES COOKIES!

07:02.089 --> 07:03.423
[ GASPS ] THAT'S IT.

07:03.457 --> 07:05.392
OUT, MONSTER!
BE GONE WITH YOU!

07:05.425 --> 07:06.594
MONSTER?

07:06.627 --> 07:09.296
BACK TO THE MOUNTAINS
FROM WHENCE YE CAME!

07:09.329 --> 07:11.298
-BOO, MONSTER!
-BOO!

07:11.331 --> 07:13.266
MONSTER?

07:14.835 --> 07:18.772
ALL RIGHT. GOT THE CHOCOLATES,
THE FLOWERS. GOOD TO GO.

07:20.173 --> 07:22.075
[ GASPS ]
OH, THAT MUST BE HER.

07:22.109 --> 07:23.243
OKAY, PANDA.

07:23.276 --> 07:25.913
THIS IS HAPPENING.

07:25.946 --> 07:29.783
EXCUSE ME, ANNIE?
I AM HERE FOR OUR DATE.

07:29.817 --> 07:31.451
HUH?
WHA--

07:31.485 --> 07:34.488
I AM ANNIE,
BUT WHO ARE -- WAIT!

07:34.522 --> 07:36.824
YOU'RE THAT GUY
FROM THE YARD SALE TODAY.

07:36.857 --> 07:38.592
YOU?
YOU'RE ANNIE?

07:38.626 --> 07:41.328
I -- I DON'T -- I-I THOUGHT --
BUT, I -- BUT THE TEXT...

07:41.361 --> 07:42.996
WHY DO YOU HAVE
MY HUSBAND'S PHONE?

07:43.030 --> 07:45.432
I AM SO SORRY.
I THINK THERE'S BEEN A MISTAKE.

07:45.465 --> 07:46.967
BABE,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

07:47.000 --> 07:49.436
I DROVE TO YOUR MOTHER'S HOUSE
TO FIND YOU AND SHE --

07:49.469 --> 07:50.771
WHO THE HECK IS THIS?

07:50.804 --> 07:53.974
CHOCOLATE? FLOWERS?
AND IS THAT MY PHONE?

07:54.007 --> 07:57.945
YOU'VE BEEN SWEET TALKIN'
MY WOMAN WITH MY OWN PHONE?

07:57.978 --> 07:59.980
PAUL, I THINK THIS IS JUST
A MISUNDERSTANDING.

08:00.013 --> 08:00.981
[ GROWLS ]

08:01.014 --> 08:02.149
OH, NO, NO, NO, NO.

08:02.182 --> 08:03.817
IT'S NOT WHAT YOU --
WHOA!

08:03.851 --> 08:06.820
YOU STEAL MY PHONE, AND NOW
YOU'RE TRYING TO STEAL MY WIFE?

08:06.854 --> 08:08.321
PAUL, NO. STOP.

08:08.355 --> 08:10.457
TH-THE PHONE.
I GOT IT AT A YARD SALE.

08:10.490 --> 08:12.459
I-I GOT A MESSAGE,
AND I THOUGHT IT WAS FOR ME.

08:12.492 --> 08:14.327
OH, I'VE GOT A MESSAGE
FOR YOU.

08:14.361 --> 08:16.530
PAUL, NO. [ GASPS ]

08:16.564 --> 08:18.532
I SWEAR I WASN'T
SWEET TALKING ANYONE.

08:18.566 --> 08:19.633
I'M NOT THAT SMOOTH.

08:19.667 --> 08:21.334
[ GROWLS ]
HONEY...

08:21.368 --> 08:22.970
THE BABY'S COMING.

08:23.003 --> 08:24.171
[ THUD ]
WHAT?

08:24.204 --> 08:25.472
BABE, W-W-WHAT'S WRONG?

08:25.505 --> 08:26.707
I THINK IT'S HAPPENING.

08:26.740 --> 08:29.009
THE BABY? UH, OH, MAN.
I'M NOT READY FOR THIS.

08:29.042 --> 08:30.878
I CAN'T HANDLE
THE RESPONSIBILITY.

08:30.911 --> 08:34.982
[ BREATHING RAPIDLY ]
OKAY, GOT TO STAY CALM.

08:35.015 --> 08:36.984
UGH.
PAUL!

08:37.017 --> 08:38.151
[ SCREAMS ]

08:38.185 --> 08:40.153
ICE BEAR FEELS
IMPENDING MOTHERHOOD NEARBY.

08:40.187 --> 08:41.321
[ SCREAMS ]

08:41.354 --> 08:43.356
HEY, BUDDY.
TIME TO WAKE UP NOW.

08:43.390 --> 08:44.992
WHERE IS MOTHER?
BROTHER!

08:45.025 --> 08:47.327
UH, THIS IS ANNIE.
HER BROKE JUST WATERED.

08:47.360 --> 08:48.495
I MEAN, UH, SHE NEEDS HELP.

08:48.528 --> 08:50.230
BREATHE.
BREATHE LIKE ICE BEAR.

08:50.263 --> 08:52.199
[ BREATHING RHYTHMICALLY ]

08:52.232 --> 08:53.567
NEED HUSBAND.
HUSBAND?

08:53.601 --> 08:55.669
HE'S KNOCKED OUT.
YOU, HUSBAND.

08:55.703 --> 08:57.838
ME? I CAN'T BE A HUSBAND.
I -- I --

08:57.871 --> 08:58.672
HUSBAND, NOW.

08:58.706 --> 09:00.440
OKAY.
W-WHAT DO I NEED TO DO?

09:00.473 --> 09:01.675
JUST HOLD YOUR HAND OR --

09:01.709 --> 09:02.843
OW!
[ SCREAMS ]

09:02.876 --> 09:03.911
THANK YOU.

09:03.944 --> 09:06.513
OW! WE HAVE TO GET A CAB
TO THE HOSPITAL.

09:06.546 --> 09:07.514
[ WOMAN SCREAMS ]

09:07.547 --> 09:09.016
OH, GET AWAY FROM ME!

09:09.049 --> 09:10.183
PLEASE, WILL YOU HELP ME?

09:10.217 --> 09:11.351
WILL ANYONE HELP A MONSTER?

09:11.384 --> 09:12.385
YOU, SIR?

09:12.419 --> 09:14.054
HELP? HELP?
[ DOG YELPS ]

09:14.087 --> 09:15.355
GRIZZ!
BROTHER!

09:15.388 --> 09:17.024
OH, I'M SO HAPPY
TO SEE YOU.

09:17.057 --> 09:18.358
I'VE HAD SUCH A CRAZY DAY.

09:18.391 --> 09:19.693
WHAT HAPPENED TO THAT GUY?

09:19.727 --> 09:21.762
GRIZZ, THIS IS ANNIE.
SHE'S HAVING A BABY.

09:21.795 --> 09:24.031
OH.
I NEED TO
GET TO THE HOSPITAL.

09:24.064 --> 09:25.098
WE NEED HELP.

09:25.132 --> 09:26.433
CAN YOU GET US A RIDE?

09:26.466 --> 09:28.702
I'M SORRY, BROTHER.
I'M A MONSTER.

09:28.736 --> 09:30.370
AND MONSTERS CAN'T HELP.

09:30.403 --> 09:32.372
THEY CAN ONLY DESTROY.

09:32.405 --> 09:34.374
NO, GRIZZ.
YOU HAVE TO SAVE US.

09:34.407 --> 09:36.209
YOU CAN BE A HERO!

09:36.243 --> 09:37.210
HERO?

09:37.244 --> 09:39.046
HERO.
YOU'RE RIGHT.

09:39.079 --> 09:41.381
IT'S TIME TO USE
THESE FISTS FOR GOOD.

09:41.414 --> 09:43.250
FOR GOOD!

09:43.283 --> 09:44.584
UM...

09:45.585 --> 09:49.256
I AM NOT A MONSTER!

09:49.289 --> 09:51.424
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

09:51.458 --> 09:53.226
WHAT THE...?

09:53.260 --> 09:55.062
HOSPITAL.
STEP ON IT.

09:55.095 --> 09:56.797
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

09:59.166 --> 10:01.068
[ GRUNTS ]
CHAIR!

10:01.101 --> 10:02.803
[ GRUNTS ]

10:02.836 --> 10:04.604
[ LAUGHS ]
FOLLOW ME!

10:04.638 --> 10:06.106
[ GRUNTS ]

10:07.440 --> 10:08.575
TAKE THAT.

10:08.608 --> 10:10.410
AND THAT. AND THAT.

10:10.443 --> 10:12.780
AND THAT. AND THAT.

10:12.813 --> 10:15.949
AND THAT.
I AM NOW MAKING
THE PRIMARY INCISION.

10:17.517 --> 10:19.319
A-HA!

10:19.352 --> 10:20.788
OH.

10:20.821 --> 10:22.255
[ BELL RINGING ]
EXCUSE ME! MA'AM!

10:22.289 --> 10:24.792
MISS! LADY!
MISS NURSE LADY! MA'AM!

10:24.825 --> 10:27.427
SIR, YOU'LL HAVE TO SIGN IN
AND WAIT LIKE EVERYBODY --

10:27.460 --> 10:28.762
[GASPS] OH, GOSH!
YOUR HANDS!

10:28.796 --> 10:30.664
WE'LL GET YOU INTO
THE E.R. STAT.

10:30.698 --> 10:32.299
OH, NO, NO, NO.
NOT ME.

10:32.332 --> 10:33.600
THIS LADY'S HAVING A BABY.

10:33.633 --> 10:34.768
[ BREATHING RHYTHMICALLY ]

10:34.802 --> 10:36.970
EASY,
ALMOST TO THE TOP.

10:37.004 --> 10:40.774
AND -- AW, DANG IT.
THIS THIS IS RIGGED. AAH!

10:40.808 --> 10:43.476
EXCUSE ME. THE COUPLE
WOULD LIKE TO SEE YOU NOW.

10:43.510 --> 10:45.178
HELLO.

10:45.212 --> 10:46.680
HEY.
PLEASE COME IN.

10:46.714 --> 10:49.116
WE JUST WANTED TO THANK YOU
SO MUCH FOR YOUR HELP

10:49.149 --> 10:51.451
AND WE'RE SORRY FOR
THE MISUNDERSTANDING

10:51.484 --> 10:52.452
AT THE CAFé.

10:52.485 --> 10:53.486
AREN'T WE, HONEY?

10:53.520 --> 10:54.822
UH, YEAH.

10:54.855 --> 10:57.457
I GOT A LITTLE HOTHEADED,
BUT I'M SORRY.

10:57.490 --> 10:58.458
IT'S NOT PROBLEM.

10:58.491 --> 10:59.459
YOU KNOW, WE'RE ALWAYS HAPPY

10:59.492 --> 11:01.128
TO HELP A PREGNANT WOMAN
IN NEED.

11:01.161 --> 11:03.463
SPEAKING OF WHICH, LET'S SEE
THAT LITTLE BUNDLE OF JOY.

11:03.496 --> 11:06.466
HEY, THERE, LITTLE GUY.
HI.

11:06.499 --> 11:07.667
[ GIGGLES ]

11:07.701 --> 11:10.637
[ CHUCKLES ]
AH, GOT A PRETTY GOOD GRIP.

11:10.670 --> 11:11.872
[ THUNK! ]

11:11.905 --> 11:13.006
STRONG BABY.

11:36.063 --> 11:40.000
[ VIDEO GAME MUSIC PLAYS ]
MMMM...

11:40.033 --> 11:41.668
OH, OH, OH!
HA-HA!

11:41.701 --> 11:42.870
HERE I COME!

11:42.903 --> 11:44.671
BOOM!
EAT THAT!

11:44.704 --> 11:46.173
[ CHEERING ]
OH, WHY DID YOU DO THAT?

11:46.206 --> 11:47.174
I WAS DOING SO WELL!

11:47.207 --> 11:48.541
HA! THIS ISN'T
A FRIENDLY GAME!

11:48.575 --> 11:50.077
IT'S A COMPETITION.

11:50.110 --> 11:52.212
Man: I'M SORRY JESSICA.
STRUT YOUR BUTT AWAY.

11:52.245 --> 11:54.214
HUH? NO!
YOU CAN'T VOTE JESSICA OFF!

11:54.247 --> 11:55.715
OH, THIS SHOW IS RIGGED!

11:55.749 --> 11:57.017
[ GROANS ]

11:57.050 --> 11:58.385
ICE BEAR ICE BEAR MADE
KOREAN PANCAKES.

11:58.418 --> 12:01.688
WHOA! THIS IS THE PERFECT FOOD
FOR RAINY DAYS.

12:01.721 --> 12:03.256
HOW'D YOU KNOW?
ICE BEAR ICE READS.

12:03.290 --> 12:05.725
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]
[ ALL SCREAM ]

12:08.428 --> 12:09.863
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

12:09.897 --> 12:11.865
AHH, OH, I LOVE
THE SMELL OF RAIN!

12:11.899 --> 12:14.367
DUDE, IT'S DANGEROUS.
GET BACK IN HERE.

12:14.401 --> 12:16.770
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
IT'S ONLY RAIN.

12:16.804 --> 12:19.539
AH. OW, OW, OW!
HARD RAIN!

12:19.572 --> 12:20.540
IT'S HAILING.

12:20.573 --> 12:22.209
UH, I'M GOING INSIDE.

12:22.242 --> 12:23.210
AAAAH!

12:23.243 --> 12:24.411
KEEP THE DOORS SHUT, GUYS.

12:24.444 --> 12:26.246
IT'S DANGEROUS OUT THERE.

12:28.281 --> 12:29.783
COME ON.

12:29.817 --> 12:31.551
THERE IS A LOW-PRESSURE SYSTEM
BUILDING

12:31.584 --> 12:33.753
THAT IS CAUSING MAJOR SHIFTS
IN THIS AREA.

12:33.787 --> 12:35.622
PEOPLE HAVE BEEN TOLD
TO STAY INSIDE

12:35.655 --> 12:37.557
AND PREPARE FOR
POSSIBLE EVACUATION.

12:37.590 --> 12:38.892
UM, THIS LOOKS REALLY BAD.

12:38.926 --> 12:40.460
HOW'S CHLOE GONNA GET HOME?

12:40.493 --> 12:41.929
I'LL JUST WAIT IT OUT.

12:41.962 --> 12:44.731
AGAIN, WE URGE
ALL TO PLEASE STAY INSIDE.

12:44.764 --> 12:47.067
UH,
LET ME ASK MY PARENTS.

12:47.100 --> 12:48.401
[ RING TONE PLAYS ]

12:48.435 --> 12:50.804
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]
MAN, IT'S GETTING BAD.

12:50.838 --> 12:51.805
THERE THEY ARE.

12:51.839 --> 12:53.974
[ SPEAKING KOREAN ]

12:54.007 --> 12:55.575
[ FEEDBACK SCREECHES ]

12:55.608 --> 12:57.577
WHOA, DAD,
YOU'RE WAY TOO CLOSE.

12:57.610 --> 12:58.912
ANN YOUNG HA SE OH!

12:58.946 --> 13:00.513
HI!
ANNYEON HASHIMNIKKA.

13:00.547 --> 13:02.315
ICE BEAR, TTO INSA DURIMNIDA.

13:02.349 --> 13:03.750
HI.
HI.

13:03.783 --> 13:05.252
IS IT RAINING
PRETTY HARD THERE, TOO?

13:05.285 --> 13:07.087
YEAH, IT'S PRETTY BAD
OVER HERE.

13:07.120 --> 13:09.089
WE'LL COME PICK YOU UP
WHEN IT STOPS RAINING.

13:09.122 --> 13:11.424
UH, THEY SAY THE RAIN
IS GONNA GET WORSE.

13:11.458 --> 13:14.094
YEAH, I DON'T THINK IT'S A GOOD
IDEA TO DRIVE ANY TIME SOON.

13:14.127 --> 13:17.097
MM...I COULD JUST STAY WITH
THE BEARS FOR THE NIGHT.

13:17.130 --> 13:19.099
IS THAT COOL?
YEAH! OF COURSE!

13:19.132 --> 13:20.968
[ FEEDBACK SCREECHES ]
NO! NO, NO, NO, NO, NO!

13:21.001 --> 13:22.502
GEEZ, DAD, STAY AWAY
FROM THE MIKE, PLEASE!

13:22.535 --> 13:25.105
I-I DON'T KNOW IF CHLOE
CAN STAY IN A CAVE.

13:25.138 --> 13:26.606
IT CAN BE TOO COLD FOR HER.

13:26.639 --> 13:29.342
[ SPEAKING KOREAN ]

13:29.376 --> 13:32.179
DAD, PLEASE,
I CAN TAKE CARE OF MYSELF.

13:32.212 --> 13:34.514
DON'T WORRY, MR. PARK.
YOUR DAUGHTER IS SAFE WITH US.

13:34.547 --> 13:36.950
COME ON, DAD, I'M WITH
THREE BEARS AT THEIR HOME.

13:36.984 --> 13:38.285
WHAT COULD BE SAFER?

13:38.318 --> 13:41.454
ICE BEAR, DEADLIEST BEAR
IN THE WORLD, SAFE.

13:41.488 --> 13:42.956
[ SIGHS ]

13:42.990 --> 13:45.358
ALL RIGHT, BUT YOU HAVE TO
PROMISE ME --

13:45.392 --> 13:47.660
BEARS, COME CLOSER.

13:47.694 --> 13:48.996
OW!

13:49.029 --> 13:50.830
YOU PROMISE
TO PROTECT OUR DAUGHTER.

13:50.864 --> 13:52.966
SHE'S THE MOST IMPORTANT
THING TO US.

13:53.000 --> 13:54.134
UGH.

13:54.167 --> 13:55.802
CAN YOU HANDLE
THIS RESPONSIBILITY?

13:55.835 --> 13:56.970
YES, SIR!

13:57.004 --> 13:58.205
WE'LL DO OUR BEST,
MR. P.

13:58.238 --> 13:59.973
ICE BEAR WILL BE
ULTIMATE PROTECTOR.

14:00.007 --> 14:02.209
[ SPEAKING KOREAN ]

14:02.242 --> 14:04.144
DON'T WORRY BEARS.
WE TRUST YOU.

14:04.177 --> 14:06.479
JUST CALL US IF
ANYTHING HAPPENS, OKAY?

14:06.513 --> 14:07.714
YOU CAN COUNT ON US,
MA'AM.

14:07.747 --> 14:09.149
OKAY. HAVE FUN.

14:09.182 --> 14:11.351
Dad: CHLOE, DON'T FORGET
TO BRUSH YOUR TEETH.

14:11.384 --> 14:14.154
DAD, PLEASE.
AND MAKE SURE
YOU CHECK YOUR PHONE.

14:14.187 --> 14:15.722
OKAY, OKAY!
I'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.

14:15.755 --> 14:17.824
AND WASH YOUR FACE,
TOO, OKAY?

14:17.857 --> 14:19.226
-LOVE YOU.
-BYE!

14:19.259 --> 14:20.327
WHOO-HOO!

14:20.360 --> 14:21.828
All: SLUMBER PARTY!

14:21.861 --> 14:24.731
* WE ARE THE FUTURE
IN CELESTIAL *

14:24.764 --> 14:27.534
* WRESTLE COSMOLOGICAL
WHOO!

14:27.567 --> 14:29.836
* TO THE STARS
AAAAAH!

14:29.869 --> 14:32.172
* CELESTIAL HERE WE GO

14:32.205 --> 14:35.742
* VIRTUES OF THE SPIRIT
OH, MAN.
WHAT COULD IT BE?

14:35.775 --> 14:37.510
OH, HO, HO, WHAT IS IT?

14:37.544 --> 14:39.913
* HOLDING HANDS,
EMBRACE OUR FUTURE *
HERE YOU GO.

14:39.947 --> 14:44.217
* IN OUR EYES FOREVER

14:44.251 --> 14:47.587
* WE ARE THE FUTURE
IN CELESTIAL *

14:47.620 --> 14:49.356
* WRESTLE COSMOLOGICAL

14:49.389 --> 14:53.426
Chloe: SO, HERE'S THE STORY
OF THE SLUG MAN.

14:53.460 --> 14:56.529
IT WAS A RAINY DAY,
JUST LIKE THIS.

14:56.563 --> 15:01.734
I WAS IN THE BATHROOM WHEN
I NOTICED SOMETHING UNUSUAL!

15:01.768 --> 15:05.738
A BUNCH OF SLUGS WERE
CRAWLING ALL OVER THE WINDOW.

15:05.772 --> 15:07.040
EW!

15:07.074 --> 15:09.209
AND THAT'S WHEN I NOTICED
THIS TRAIL,

15:09.242 --> 15:14.547
A SLIMY MUCOUS TRAIL
THAT LED TO MY ROOM.

15:14.581 --> 15:15.715
UHHH...

15:15.748 --> 15:17.050
I DON'T LIKE
WHERE THIS IS GOING.

15:17.084 --> 15:18.885
SUSPENSE.
ICE BEAR DOESN'T LIKE.

15:18.918 --> 15:20.387
I KNEW SOMEONE WAS IN MY ROOM.

15:20.420 --> 15:23.723
IT WAS MAKING THIS
REALLY DISTURBING NOISE.

15:23.756 --> 15:26.293
[ IMITATES CRUNCHING SOUND ]

15:26.326 --> 15:27.560
[ WHIMPERS ]

15:27.594 --> 15:30.730
SO I WENT INTO THE KITCHEN
AND GRABBED A FLASHLIGHT,

15:30.763 --> 15:34.134
AND SLOWLY I OPENED
MY BEDROOM DOOR.

15:34.167 --> 15:36.069
IT WAS TOO DARK TO SEE ANYTHING,

15:36.103 --> 15:38.471
BUT I KNEW SOMETHING
WAS TERRIBLY WRONG.

15:38.505 --> 15:41.908
THIS STENCH
WAS FILLING MY ROOM --

15:41.941 --> 15:44.077
LIKE SOMEONE WAS ROTTING!

15:44.111 --> 15:47.280
RIGHT THEN, I SAW SOMETHING
SLOWLY RISE,

15:47.314 --> 15:50.317
AND THERE IT WAS --
THE SLUG MAN LAYING IN MY BED...

15:50.350 --> 15:51.918
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]
[ SCREAMS ]

15:51.951 --> 15:53.420
[ SMACKS LIPS ]

15:53.453 --> 15:58.158
...SMACKING ITS LIPS,
READY TO DEVOUR ME.

15:58.191 --> 15:59.759
THE END!

15:59.792 --> 16:01.094
MAN,
THAT WAS A CRAZY STORY.

16:01.128 --> 16:02.295
ICE BEAR IS SCARED.

16:02.329 --> 16:04.331
W-W-W-WHAT IF THE SLUGMAN
GETS US TONIGHT?

16:04.364 --> 16:06.666
OH, COME ON.
IT WAS JUST A MADE UP STORY.

16:06.699 --> 16:08.001
YOU SURE?
YEP.

16:08.035 --> 16:09.502
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]
[ ALL GASP ]

16:09.536 --> 16:13.440
OH, MAN, I REALLY HOPE
THIS STORM GOES AWAY SOON.

16:13.473 --> 16:14.807
[ RUSTLING ]
AAH! DID YOU HEAR THAT?

16:14.841 --> 16:16.276
HEAR WHAT?

16:16.309 --> 16:18.178
[ RUSTLING CONTINUES ]
AAH! THERE IT IS AGAIN!

16:19.979 --> 16:21.114
HELLO?

16:21.148 --> 16:22.782
[ RUSTLING ]
[ ALL SCREAM ]

16:22.815 --> 16:24.151
I THINK
THE SLUGMAN'S AFTER US.

16:24.184 --> 16:25.152
I DON'T WANT TO BE
SLUG FOOD!

16:25.185 --> 16:26.286
SHH!
DON'T LET HIM HEAR US!

16:26.319 --> 16:27.520
ICE BEAR WANTS TO LIVE.

16:27.554 --> 16:29.489
PANDA, LISTEN!
THERE IS NO SLUG MAN --

16:29.522 --> 16:32.492
THAT WAS JUST AN OLD STORY
WE USED TO TELL AT SUMMER CAMP.

16:32.525 --> 16:33.660
BUT THE NOISES.

16:33.693 --> 16:34.661
IT'S JUST THE RAIN.

16:34.694 --> 16:36.329
[ THUD, GLASS SHATTERS ]

16:38.398 --> 16:39.999
[ ALL SCREAM ]
IT'S THE SLUG MAN!

16:40.033 --> 16:41.334
GRAB CHLOE!
MOVE, MOVE!

16:41.368 --> 16:42.335
WAIT! WAIT UP!

16:42.369 --> 16:44.003
WHOA, GUYS! WAIT!

16:45.738 --> 16:47.974
OKAY, SECURE THE ROOM!
STAY RIGHT HERE, CHLOE!

16:48.007 --> 16:49.142
CONTAINING THE CHLOE.

16:49.176 --> 16:51.511
WAIT, BUT WE --
HEY, GUYS -- UGH!

16:51.544 --> 16:53.180
DON'T WORRY, CHLOE.
WE GOT YOU.

16:53.213 --> 16:54.647
STOP!
JUST LISTEN!

16:54.681 --> 16:56.483
NO. IT'S NOT SAFE
OUT THERE, CHLOE.

16:56.516 --> 16:58.985
YOU ARE OUR SWEET BABY ANGEL,
AND WE MADE A PROMISE

16:59.018 --> 17:01.254
TO YOUR FATHER TO KEEP YOU SAFE.
IT'S OUR DUTY.

17:01.288 --> 17:03.390
GRIZZ, COME ON.
IT'S THE RAIN MAKING THAT NOISE.

17:03.423 --> 17:05.558
HUSH, SWEET CHILD.
YOU'RE DELIRIOUS FROM FEAR.

17:05.592 --> 17:07.160
WE'VE GOT THIS
COMPLETELY UNDER CONTROL.

17:07.194 --> 17:08.495
I'M JUST GONNA
BORROW THIS FOR A SEC.

17:08.528 --> 17:10.330
I'M GONNA GIVE YOUR DAD
A QUICK UPDATE.

17:10.363 --> 17:11.164
HUH?

17:11.198 --> 17:12.332
[ GASPS ] NO SERVICE?

17:12.365 --> 17:13.833
PANPAN,
CALL MR. CHLOE'S DAD.

17:13.866 --> 17:15.868
YEAH, SURE.

17:16.869 --> 17:19.239
I THINK MY PHONE IS STILL
IN THE LIVING ROOM, GRIZZ.

17:19.272 --> 17:21.174
I CAN GO GET IT.
GOOD IDEA, CHLOE.

17:21.208 --> 17:22.742
ONE OF US --
NOT YOU, THOUGH --

17:22.775 --> 17:24.177
IS GOING TO HAVE TO
INVESTIGATE.

17:24.211 --> 17:26.846
THE PRETZELS
WILL DECIDE OUR FATE.

17:26.879 --> 17:27.847
LITTLE BRO.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.416
PANPAN.

17:29.449 --> 17:30.850
[ WHIMPERS ]

17:30.883 --> 17:32.185
BE STRONG, PANDA.

17:32.219 --> 17:34.721
ICE BEAR WILL TELL TALE
OF BRAVE BROTHER.

17:34.754 --> 17:36.389
OH, PLEASE.

17:37.257 --> 17:38.525
[ DOOR HINGES CREAK ]

17:38.558 --> 17:40.560
[ WHIMPERS ]

17:40.593 --> 17:42.429
[ GROANS ]

17:45.898 --> 17:47.867
[ WHIMPERS ]

17:47.900 --> 17:49.035
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

17:49.068 --> 17:50.937
[ SCREAMS ]
I COULDN'T GET THE PHONE!

17:50.970 --> 17:52.739
I'M PRETTY SURE
SOMETHING'S OUT THERE.

17:52.772 --> 17:54.040
IT MIGHT HAVE BREATHED ON ME.

17:54.073 --> 17:55.708
SERIOUSLY, GUYS.
LET ME GO OUT THERE.

17:55.742 --> 17:58.545
IT'S JUST THE STORM MAKING
NOISE, NOTHING TO BE AFRAID OF.

17:58.578 --> 18:01.281
NO, YOU CAN'T GO OUT ALONE.
WE'LL GO TOGETHER.

18:03.583 --> 18:05.652
COME ON.

18:08.421 --> 18:09.789
WHOA!

18:09.822 --> 18:12.259
I THINK
WE SHOULD SPLIT UP.

18:15.428 --> 18:17.096
HUH!

18:19.299 --> 18:20.733
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

18:20.767 --> 18:22.735
[ PANTING ]

18:22.769 --> 18:24.671
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

18:26.806 --> 18:29.075
MM...

18:29.108 --> 18:31.411
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]
AAAAH!

18:31.444 --> 18:32.412
OOF!

18:32.445 --> 18:33.413
[ SIGHS ]

18:33.446 --> 18:34.647
HELP.

18:36.849 --> 18:38.451
HA! GUYS, FOUND IT!

18:38.485 --> 18:39.452
QUICK, PASS IT HERE.

18:39.486 --> 18:40.920
OH, NO.

18:40.953 --> 18:42.755
THE BATTERY IS DEAD.

18:42.789 --> 18:44.291
[ CRASH ]

18:48.528 --> 18:50.763
[ ALL SCREAMING ]
BACK TO THE SAFE ROOM!

18:50.797 --> 18:53.166
Chloe: [ Muffled ]
HEY, GUYS, STOP! STOP!

18:58.471 --> 19:00.106
BREAK! HEY, CHLOE ARE YOU --
WHERE'S CHLOE?!

19:00.139 --> 19:01.441
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]
[ CHLOE SCREAMS ]

19:01.474 --> 19:03.843
All: CHLOE!
WE'RE COMING, CHLOE!

19:03.876 --> 19:05.278
OH, HEY, GUYS.

19:05.312 --> 19:07.447
CHLOE, YOU'RE OKAY.
WAIT, WHY WERE YOU SCREAMING?

19:07.480 --> 19:09.782
BECAUSE I FOUND
YOUR INTRUDER RIGHT...

19:09.816 --> 19:11.284
[ ALL SCREAM ]
...HERE!

19:11.318 --> 19:13.286
JUST A CONFUSED LITTLE RACCOON.

19:13.320 --> 19:14.787
I TOLD YOU IT WAS NOTHING.

19:14.821 --> 19:15.788
OH.

19:15.822 --> 19:17.290
[ ALL CHUCKLE ]

19:17.324 --> 19:20.293
BE FREE, LITTLE DUDE.

19:20.327 --> 19:22.329
SEE, EVERYONE ALWAYS TRYING
TO PROTECT ME,

19:22.362 --> 19:23.963
BUT I CAN HANDLE THINGS MYSELF.

19:23.996 --> 19:25.798
I DON'T NEED TO BE BABIED
ALL THE TIME.

19:25.832 --> 19:28.468
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

19:28.501 --> 19:30.169
[ LIGHT SWITCH CLICKS ]
THE POWER'S OUT.

19:30.203 --> 19:31.304
AND OUR PHONES ARE DEAD.

19:31.338 --> 19:32.705
ICE BEAR DOES NOT LIKE
STORMS.

19:32.739 --> 19:34.140
GUYS, GUYS, CALM DOWN!

19:34.173 --> 19:35.975
IT'S JUST A POWER OUTAGE
'CAUSE OF THE WEATHER.

19:36.008 --> 19:37.143
WE JUST NEED TO --

19:37.176 --> 19:39.479
[ RUSTLING ]
UHH...WHAT WAS THAT?

19:39.512 --> 19:40.980
IT'S COMING FROM OUTSIDE.

19:41.013 --> 19:42.315
[ WHIMPERS ]

19:42.349 --> 19:44.317
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]
I-I'M SURE IT'S NOTHING.

19:44.351 --> 19:47.554
JUST ANOTHER RACCOON
OR A MOOSE OR SOMETHING.

19:47.587 --> 19:48.655
[ RUSTLING ]

19:48.688 --> 19:50.990
MAYBE THE WIND
KNOCKED SOMETHING OVER?

19:51.023 --> 19:53.326
[ RUSTLING CONTINUES ]

19:53.360 --> 19:54.827
SOMETHING'S OUT THERE.

19:54.861 --> 19:57.564
IT WAS PROBABLY JUST
A BRANCH IN THE WIND, GRIZZ.

19:57.597 --> 20:00.500
THERE'S NOTHING OUT THERE
TO BE AFRAID OF.

20:00.533 --> 20:01.334
SEE?

20:01.368 --> 20:02.502
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

20:02.535 --> 20:05.004
[ ALL SCREAM ]
SLUG MAN!

20:05.037 --> 20:07.840
CHLOE, HEAD TO MY ROOM!
[ SCREAMS ]

20:07.874 --> 20:09.008
CHLOE, ARE YOU OKAY!

20:09.041 --> 20:10.076
YEAH. WHAT WAS THAT?

20:10.109 --> 20:11.378
I THINK
IT WAS THE SLUG MAN.

20:11.411 --> 20:12.912
OH, MAN,
IT KNOWS WE'RE HERE.

20:12.945 --> 20:15.248
IT COULD ALREADY BE
INSIDE!

20:15.282 --> 20:16.916
[ KNOCK ON WINDOW ]

20:16.949 --> 20:19.519
IT FOUND US!
GO, GO, GO, GO!

20:19.552 --> 20:20.887
[ PANTING ]

20:20.920 --> 20:22.689
IT WAS THE SLUG MAN.

20:22.722 --> 20:23.590
WHAT DID I TELL YOU?

20:23.623 --> 20:25.258
IT'S GONNA COME FIND
AND DEVOUR US.

20:25.292 --> 20:26.693
I DON'T WANT TO BE EATEN!

20:26.726 --> 20:28.595
THERE'S SO MUCH I HAVE YET
TO DO IN THIS LIFE.

20:28.628 --> 20:30.763
ICE BEAR MOST SCARED BEAR
IN THE WORLD.

20:30.797 --> 20:32.031
WAIT, SHH.

20:32.064 --> 20:34.066
DO YOU HEAR THAT?

20:36.403 --> 20:37.737
[ DOOR HANDLE RATTLES ]

20:37.770 --> 20:38.871
[ ALL SCREAM ]

20:38.905 --> 20:41.040
SLUG MAN'S GONNA GET IN!
WE'RE DONE FOR!

20:41.073 --> 20:42.074
ICE BEAR FEARS THE WORST.

20:42.108 --> 20:43.410
Grizz: GUYS.

20:46.579 --> 20:49.382
DON'T WORRY, CHLOE.
IT'LL BE OKAY.

20:49.416 --> 20:52.084
WE MADE A PROMISE
TO KEEP CHLOE SAFE,

20:52.118 --> 20:54.887
SO LET'S GO DO OUR JOB.

20:54.921 --> 20:56.389
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

20:56.423 --> 20:58.224
PUSH, BROTHERS!
TOGETHER!

20:58.257 --> 20:59.726
[ GRUNTING ]

20:59.759 --> 21:02.128
WAIT, DOESN'T THIS DOOR
OPEN OUTWARDS?

21:02.161 --> 21:04.096
AAAAH!
OOF!

21:04.130 --> 21:05.632
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

21:05.665 --> 21:06.766
AAAAAH!

21:07.967 --> 21:09.902
[ BREATHING HOARSELY ]

21:09.936 --> 21:11.270
[ SCREAMING ]

21:12.305 --> 21:13.940
[ GASPS ]
RUN, CHLOE!

21:13.973 --> 21:15.942
SAVE YOURSELF!

21:17.844 --> 21:18.945
[ SCREAMING ]

21:22.114 --> 21:23.683
[ GRUNTS ]
[ THUD ]

21:26.453 --> 21:28.087
WHAT IS IT?
All: AAAH!

21:28.120 --> 21:29.489
OH, THE POWER'S BACK ON!

21:29.522 --> 21:32.091
WAIT, THAT'S NOT THE SLUGMAN.
IT'S A HUMAN.

21:32.124 --> 21:33.259
[ GROANS ]

21:33.292 --> 21:35.261
[ SPEAKING KOREAN ]

21:35.294 --> 21:36.929
OH, GEEZ, DAD!

21:36.963 --> 21:38.264
[ MUMBLING IN KOREAN ]

21:38.297 --> 21:39.766
DAD! ARE YOU OKAY?

21:39.799 --> 21:40.600
OH, CHLOE!

21:40.633 --> 21:42.435
I'M SO SORRY
I ATTACKED YOU.

21:42.469 --> 21:44.270
WHAT ARE YOU EVEN
DOING HERE?

21:44.303 --> 21:46.439
I WAS WORRIED,
SO I CAME TO GET YOU.

21:46.473 --> 21:48.307
I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE
DANGEROUS HERE,

21:48.341 --> 21:50.109
BUT [SIGHS]

21:50.142 --> 21:52.278
I GUESS
I WAS WORRYING TOO MUCH.

21:52.311 --> 21:55.114
[ LAUGHS ]
I ACTUALLY WAS REALLY SCARED.

21:55.147 --> 21:56.483
I'M GLAD YOU CAME, DAD.

21:58.651 --> 22:01.521
UM, HELLO, MR. PARK.
SORRY FOR THE MISUNDERSTANDING.

22:01.554 --> 22:03.856
AND SCREAMING.
YEAH, AND ALL THE SCREAMING.

22:03.890 --> 22:06.493
WE WERE ALL JUST FREAKING OUT
AT A SCARY STORY.

22:06.526 --> 22:08.828
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

22:08.861 --> 22:11.798
MAYBE YOU SHOULD STAY
UNTIL THE STORM STOPS.

22:11.831 --> 22:14.967
* WE ARE THE FUTURE
IN CELESTIAL *

22:15.001 --> 22:17.470
* WRESTLE COSMOLOGICAL

22:17.504 --> 22:19.672
* TO THE STARS

22:24.677 --> 22:26.913
**

22:36.188 --> 22:37.857
[ KEYS CLACKING ]
DONE!

22:37.890 --> 22:39.258
DONE.DONE!
